Class Operator

java.lang.Object
  core.planner.Operator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Standardizable, java.lang.Cloneable
public final class Operator
extends java.lang.Object
implements Standardizable, java.lang.Cloneable

The Operator class implements an operator. This class stores the preconditions the delete effects and the add effects.
